  <h1>About CalcStack</h1>

  <section class="content-section">
    <p>
      CalcStack is a free financial calculator platform built for people in <strong>India, UAE, and the United States</strong>. We build interactive tools that help you make better financial decisions — from SIP planning to tax optimization to property investment analysis.
    </p>

    <h2>Why We Built This</h2>
    <p>
      Most financial calculator sites are either covered in ads that make them unusable, or they're too simple — just a formula with a single answer. We wanted tools that let you <strong>play with scenarios</strong>, compare options side-by-side, and actually understand the numbers behind your financial decisions.
    </p>
    <p>
      Every calculator on CalcStack is:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Interactive</strong> — sliders, real-time updates, visual charts</li>
      <li><strong>Accurate</strong> — formulas sourced from government regulations and financial standards</li>
      <li><strong>Free</strong> — no signup, no paywall, no email required</li>
      <li><strong>Transparent</strong> — we show the formula and explain the math</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Our Data Sources</h2>
    <p>We source our rates, tax slabs, and regulatory information from official government publications:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>India:</strong> Income Tax Department (incometax.gov.in), SEBI, RBI, Ministry of Finance quarterly notifications</li>
      <li><strong>UAE:</strong> Ministry of Human Resources (MOHRE), Federal Tax Authority, Dubai Land Department</li>
      <li><strong>US:</strong> IRS.gov, Federal Reserve, Bureau of Labor Statistics</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Rates are reviewed and updated quarterly. The "last verified" date on each calculator shows when we last confirmed the data.</p>

    <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
    <p>
      Some pages contain affiliate links to financial products and services. If you sign up through these links, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you. This helps us keep the calculators free. <strong>Affiliate relationships never influence our calculator results or recommendations.</strong>
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
